Package model.dao

Provides all dao objects from database.
For every object in the business logic package we provide an interface made to interact with the database. For exemple TrainingDao is an interface which can create, update, delete, and get a training from the data base. We don't have to know how the database his made. His implementation TrainingDaoImpl made the sql request, but if maybe one day a no-sql database. We'll just have to add another implemation for all the interface.
